
 <div class="fondo-show-spot">
 <div class="container">
  <div class =" show-card d-flex justify-content-between">
    <div class ="mt-3 ">
      <h1><%= @item.name.capitalize %></h1>
    </div>
  </div>


  <% images = @item.images.map {|image| image.key}%>
  <% images_processed = []%>
  <% until images.empty? %>
    <% random = rand(1..3) %>
    <% images_processed.push(images.slice(0,random)) %>
    <% images = images.drop(random) %>
  <% end %>
  <div class="row-grid mt-0">
    <% images_processed.each do |slice| %>
      <div class="column-grid" style="max-width: <%= 100/images_processed.length%>%">
        <% slice.each do |image| %>
          <%= cl_image_tag image, width: 1180, height: 1050, crop: :fit, :style =>"width:100%"%>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class ="row vh-80 mt-5">
    <div class="col vertical-scroll">
      <div id ="description">
        <div class=" ">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Description</h3>
          <hr>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Sint quibusdam ipsam consectetur nisi quo, placeat sequi voluptatibus iusto quos cupiditate saepe amet qui! Qui accusamus cumque consectetur nemo dicta suscipit?Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Neque deleniti commodi ipsum. Id facilis iusto, rem assumenda quos animi amet illo ad sit, perferendis ab veniam, alias expedita voluptates totam Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel nulla dolor molestiae aperiam minima officia perferendis enim praesentium. Quia omnis possimus dicta ab commodi aperiam architecto maiores consequatur temporibus suscipit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Deserunt nam dolores laudantium, delectus vel explicabo voluptatum soluta qui vitae velit excepturi, nisi illo hic maxime voluptatibus deleniti autem rerum eveniet? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rem eaque quis accusantium provident consectetur, harum odit eligendi. Veniam saepe eveniet voluptatem facere eius dicta assumenda quidem vel, corporis tempore iure.
          <%= @item.description%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col vertical-scroll">
      <div id ="quantity">
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Cantidad:</h3>
          <hr>
          <%= @item.quantity%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id ="type">
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Tipo</h3>
          <hr>
          <%= @item.subtype.type.name%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id ="Subtype">
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Subtipo</h3>
          <hr>
          <%= @item.subtype.name%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id ="Price">
        <div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Precio</h3>
          <hr>
          <%= @item.price%> soles
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 20px; ">Reservar:</h3>
        <hr>

      </div>
      <%= simple_form_for [@item,@reservation], :html => {:class => "form-group row"} do |f| %>
          <div class="col">
            <%= f.input :quantity, :class => "form-control"%>
          </div>
          <div class="col pt-1">
            <%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-primary mt-4" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
